1
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,680
Ah!

2
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:35,000
That scared me to death!

3
00:01:36,960 --> 00:01:39,200
Hahaha!

4
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,240
I told you not to go.

5
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:42,200
Look,

6
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,729
there really are monsters.

7
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,530
It's all your fault.

8
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,000
Ouch!

9
00:01:53,039 --> 00:01:54,240
Linglong, what's wrong?

10
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:56,240
I think I sprained my ankle just now.

11
00:01:58,720 --> 00:01:59,720
What should we do?

12
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:01,240
What should we do?

13
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,760
Ask him to carry you on his back.

14
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:04,480
Don't you know how to be tender to a lady?

15
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,520
This Xu Zhinian

16
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:07,040
is really thick-headed.

17
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:08,680
If he doesn't take the initiative,

18
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:09,960
you have to.

19
00:02:11,920 --> 00:02:12,800
Zhinian.

20
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,760
Can you

21
00:02:15,440 --> 00:02:16,640
carry me on your back?

22
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:22,520
Yes.

23
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,079
Get on.

24
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,010
Mr. Charles,

25
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:41,660
come on,

26
00:02:42,920 --> 00:02:43,720
have some tea.

27
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,600
I have been doing business in China for years,

28
00:02:46,600 --> 00:02:48,120
and I have never been insulted like this.

29
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:50,000
Hu Linglong represents your Hu family,

30
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:52,130
while I represent our British Empire.

31
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,840
Hu Linglong's misbehavior

32
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:54,800
means the Hu family is

33
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,440
making an enemy of the British Empire.

34
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:57,840
Oh, Mr. Charles,

35
00:02:58,240 --> 00:03:00,000
you exaggerate.

36
00:03:00,480 --> 00:03:01,440
How could our Hu family

37
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,880
dare to disrespect you?

38
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:04,120
As long as you are willing

39
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,920
to cooperate with the Hu family again,

40
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:06,880
we can accept

41
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,040
any condition.

42
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,560
I want Hu Linglong

43
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,640
to go to our British firm

44
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:12,700
and apologize outside the main gate.

45
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,480
I want to let others know

46
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:15,960
the consequences of challenging

47
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,890
the dignity of the British Empire.

48
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,040
This...

49
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:22,120
Well...

50
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,680
Mr. Charles...

51
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:31,480
Hey, boss,

52
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:32,480
how much is this?

53
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,040
Zhinian,

54
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,680
I want to take a look over there,

55
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,640
put me down.

56
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:37,320
Okay.

57
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,800
Miss, do you see anything you like?

58
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:45,520
Take a look.

59
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,320
Ah, Mr. Xu,

60
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:48,440
it's been a while.

61
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:50,640
Why are you here to buy jewelry again today?

62
00:03:50,640 --> 00:03:52,700
Who else have you bought jewelry for?

63
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,760
Which one do you like?

64
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:01,450
I like this hairpin.

65
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,500
Let me put it on for you.

66
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,640
Hu Linglong,

67
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:12,120
this time I've got something on you.

68
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:16,360
It looks beautiful.

69
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:18,200
What a perfect match.

70
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:20,760
Boss,

71
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:22,480
how much is this hairpin?

72
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,400
I'm sorry,

73
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:25,000
this hairpin was reserved by someone else.

74
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,800
I left it on the counter and forgot to put it away.

75
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,160
I'm really sorry.

76
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:31,520
Do you have another one exactly like this?

77
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:32,200
These goods

78
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:34,000
were brought from Guangzhou.

79
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:36,580
It's the only one in the whole county.

80
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:38,520
Mm.

81
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:43,040
Brother, sister,

82
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:45,280
could you spare some money for me?

83
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,560
My mother and I have nothing to eat.

84
00:04:51,840 --> 00:04:52,480
Child,

85
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,280
say thank you.

86
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:55,440
Thank you, brother and sister.

87
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:58,000
Thank you.

88
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,000
In this world today,

89
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:06,020
the people are destitute,

90
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,800
and public morality is not what it used to be.

91
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:10,280
If I were born in an ordinary family,

92
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,280
wouldn't I end up with

93
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,480
a fate similar to

94
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,800
that little girl's?

95
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:17,220
That is why I went to study in Britain.

96
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,920
Now, returning to the Beiyang Fleet

97
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:22,120
is exactly to do my meager part

98
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:24,640
to turn this world upside down

99
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:28,500
and let everyone live a life with enough food and clothing.

100
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:29,200
Zhinian,

101
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:30,770
I believe in you.

102
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:33,360
Yeah.

103
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:44,720
Let's go.

104
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,200
Boss,

105
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,200
order another identical one for me.

106
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:56,800
Okay.

107
00:06:01,280 --> 00:06:08,000
Since childhood,

108
00:06:08,880 --> 00:06:15,440
born with a strong temper,

109
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:25,200
loyal and devoted to helping the King of Han.

110
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:30,380
Why are you in such a hurry?

111
00:06:30,520 --> 00:06:31,580
There's good news.

112
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,200
Yesterday, when I passed by the county town,

113
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:34,280
at that jewelry shop,

114
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:35,800
I saw Xu Zhinian giving Hu Linglong

115
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:37,080
a silver hairpin.

116
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:38,520
The two of them were very sweet.

117
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:40,120
They must be having an affair.

118
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:40,520
Oh.

119
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:41,080
Right,

120
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:43,810
the shopkeeper of that jewelry shop can testify.

121
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,200
Hu Linglong

122
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,960
once swore in the Hu family ancestral hall

123
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:48,880
never to marry.

124
00:06:49,520 --> 00:06:50,800
Am I remembering it right?

125
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,400
Yes.

126
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,200
But now,

127
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:55,000
she is messing around with Xu Zhinian.

128
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:57,650
If the patriarch finds out about this,

129
00:06:57,880 --> 00:07:00,120
he will definitely not let her off lightly.

130
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,040
It's just that

131
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,890
we don't have any evidence now.

132
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:05,920
Don't worry,

133
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:08,720
they will expose their flaws sooner or later.

134
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:09,440
Then,

135
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,090
what do you mean, Mr. Yamamoto?

136
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:15,280
There is a boss named Zhang in Qimen County.

137
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:18,320
He has a foolish son who cannot take care of himself.

138
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:20,320
If we can make Hu Linglong marry him,

139
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,560
I think it will be very interesting.

140
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,280
Haha.

141
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,280
By then,

142
00:07:24,760 --> 00:07:26,560
you can logically

143
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:28,800
take the position of the head of the family.

144
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,040
Our cooperation

145
00:07:30,280 --> 00:07:31,810
will also go a step further.

146
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:32,800
Mr. Hu,

147
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:34,040
am I right?

148
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:36,290
Then everything

149
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,800
will follow Mr. Yamamoto's arrangements.

150
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:40,730
I will certainly do my best to help.

151
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,120
Good.

152
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:44,900
Tomorrow morning,

153
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:46,890
come with me to meet the elders.

154
00:07:53,080 --> 00:07:56,680
Linglong is truly capable of taking on great responsibilities.

155
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:57,560
Elder,

156
00:07:57,960 --> 00:08:00,020
I have an important matter to report.

157
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:01,080
Wenyi,

158
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:03,400
why are you in such a rush?

159
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,560
How about...

160
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:07,200
Let's call it a day.

161
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,160
Okay.

162
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:10,240
Farewell.

163
00:08:10,840 --> 00:08:11,880
Take care.

164
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:12,640
Goodbye.

165
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:13,240
Okay.

166
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:13,840
Farewell.

167
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:14,640
Take care.

168
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:17,120
Wenyi,

169
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:17,880
take a seat.

170
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:21,600
Elder.

171
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:26,280
Previously, Hu Linglong offended the British merchants at the tea plantation,

172
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:27,480
causing our Hu family

173
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:29,450
to lose over half of our tea orders.

174
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,679
They are now willing to resume trading,

175
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:33,799
but they demand

176
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:37,280
that Hu Linglong go to the foreign firm's front door

177
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:39,280
to plead guilty and commit suicide.

178
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:42,780
About this matter you mentioned,

179
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,810
I already know about it.

180
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:48,840
The foreigners care about their pride,

181
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:51,020
but doesn't the Hu family's pride

182
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:51,840
matter too?

183
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,240
Oh.

184
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,200
Besides,

185
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:55,840
Linglong is now

186
00:08:56,160 --> 00:08:57,560
also our Hu family's

187
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,200
current head.

188
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,000
Her dignity

189
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,720
represents our Hu family.

190
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,360
Why should she

191
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:07,560
plead guilty to the foreigners?

192
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,280
Elder.

193
00:09:09,800 --> 00:09:10,840
This Hu family tea

194
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,800
is the foundation of the Hu family.

195
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:14,880
You can't just ignore it.

196
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:16,800
My father is right, Elder.

197
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:17,680
Yes.

198
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,120
Hmph.

199
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,040
Elder,

200
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,360
I have another idea.

201
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:25,610
Previously,

202
00:09:26,040 --> 00:09:27,800
Mr. Yamamoto introduced me to a

203
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:28,920
merchant from Qimen,

204
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:29,920
named Boss Zhang.

205
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:32,000
He can help us open up

206
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:32,860
the tea market.

207
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:34,280
But

208
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:35,980
he has a condition.

209
00:09:36,640 --> 00:09:37,570
What condition?

210
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:38,440
They want,

211
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:40,840
want a marriage alliance with our Hu family.

212
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:41,800
Marriage alliance?

213
00:09:41,800 --> 00:09:44,640
To have Hu Linglong marry into the Zhang family.

214
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:49,850
I've heard of the Zhang family for a long time.

215
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,360
I heard

216
00:09:51,720 --> 00:09:52,960
their child

217
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,840
is a fool.

218
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:56,280
Sigh.

219
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:57,680
Hu Wenyi,

220
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,400
we absolutely cannot

221
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:03,220
marry Hu Linglong off to that kind of person.

222
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:04,400
Furthermore,

223
00:10:04,760 --> 00:10:07,120
Linglong in front of the ancestors

224
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:09,000
once made a vow

225
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,060
never to marry.

226
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:12,880
Elder,

227
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:15,280
the situation is extremely urgent.

228
00:10:15,280 --> 00:10:17,320
How can you still be considering Hu Linglong?

229
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:17,720
Ah.

230
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:20,180
Let me tell you another thing.

231
00:10:20,280 --> 00:10:22,800
The oath Hu Linglong swore in front of our ancestors,

232
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:23,800
the oath she took,

233
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:26,040
she has already broken it secretly.

234
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:28,360
I saw it with my own eyes.

235
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,240
Exactly.

236
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:30,760
What do you mean?

237
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:32,380
You don't know,

238
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:34,450
actually she and Xu Zhinian...

239
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:36,610
They've been having an affair.

240
00:10:36,800 --> 00:10:37,660
Think about it.

241
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,440
The British merchants are applying pressure,

242
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:41,000
and the Zhang family urges us daily.

243
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,480
This concerns the Hu family's legacy.

244
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:44,600
In the future,

245
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:47,320
won't everything be ruined?

246
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:59,120
You've got some nerve, Hu Linglong.

247
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,120
You won't admit it?

248
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:05,440
Then let's confront each other.

249
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:06,400
Ah,

250
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:07,880
that's more like it.
